data.description:
This home features:

Large Island in an open floor plan Kitchen, dinning living room combo and stainless steel appliances. 

There is a second dinning room with a coffered ceiling and tv room. 

Maintenance free gas fireplace. 

Luxury vinyl plank floors throughout and brand new carpet in the all the bedrooms. 

Large master bedroom with garden tub, seperate shower and large walk-in closet with custom shelving. 

This home comes with new front load washer and dryer. 

The backyard is great for children to play and family BBQ's. 

Home will be available June 1, 2023 and showings start Tuesdsay March 21, 2023.

Tenant is responsible for water, trash and sewer, gas, electric, lawn care and mandatory renters insurance. There is no smoking in the home and no pets. 

Application fee $150
First months rent plus security deposit.

Lease terms 12 months or more.

Driveway and two car garage parking. 

Unfurnished 

Furnished is available with additional lease option fee.
